description:
Good Omens was the best tv show I watched this summer and I am so glad that I finally got around to do this video. I loved watching it again while I was editing and I do hope you enjoy it, too. Happy Doomsday!

I do not own anything in this video. All rights to the owners of the clips and the music. 

The clips are from the show "Good Omens" which you can watch on Amazon Prime.

The music is Umbrella (Orange Version) by Rihanna ft. JAY-Z.
